      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine finished in a deep, lustrous obsidian that swallows the light. Imagine winding through coastal roads, the engine hum providing a baritone soundtrack to your escape. Every curve of its silhouette was sculpted for the dreamer, and the interior\u2014a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather and polished accents\u2014whispers of grand adventures yet to be written. To own this is to inherit a legacy of pure, unadulterated style. It stands as a testament to an era where driving was an art form, waiting for its next curator to take the helm.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
